item.title: Getting peoples Number?
item.dc:creator: yoyo278
item.description:
Hypno-Toad:

Well, that’s a side of Fnoigy i never knew about.

Now to the OP: Lurking around in the forums, you should expect people laughing at you for thinking one of the developer’s of Black Mesa is Summer Glau, and even worse, thinking you had a chance with Ram. Also, meeting a nice girl at your family reunion? You gotta admit, if someone else said that, i bet you would think they were inbred.

For the record, i don’t think you’re a troll, just a hipster who hasn’t spent too much time on Teh Interwebz.

EDIT: That “inbred mexican” comment… no, just no.

First of all sorry fnoigy, i wasn’t trying to upset to i just needed to vent my rage for that innapropriate comment you made earlier. if you’d be willing to apologise for that i’d be willing to do the same to you (oh and no i’m not a hacker, your just the first link that came up on bing!)

i didn’t really know what a troll was before, i thought it meant idiot but i see it has deeper concoctions and it is understandable why you’d think that, the internet is comparively new to me, my family are big on books. this was one of the first places i came apart from fb because i remember playing the original, BUT i never once called it a family reunion that was added by following readers

anyway to flip the coin on it’s head it turns out that this girl is seeing someone now, but she’s nice so i’m not going to let it get to me.

Is it possible to make another topic on advice for me here? i don’t want this topic to stray to far from the point, and if so do i need to delete this thread first and where is a good place to post it? (i’m assuming the ladies room)

thanks,

yoyo
